      <br>The Jagged Forest is now opening up on the Stormhammer Server!<br><blockquote>"This zone combines outdoor and indoor adventure areas for brave souls of 40th Level and up. Jaggedpine is currently in final testing and we plan to have it live on the server soon. Explore the mysteries of this dense forest and its reclusive inhabitants. Become embroiled with the local citizenry's conflict and town defense. Prove your alliance to the Duke of Below at his secretive temple. Whatever you choose to do, adventure surely waits!"</blockquote><br>From the sound of it, this zone will be hitting the rest of the servers eventually. (too bad Maurader's Mire has not yet)  You can read more about this by clicking <a href="http://legends.everquest.station.sony.com/newsview.jsp?o=43991">here</a></font></p>
