      </b><font face="Arial" size="2"><font color="#FFC164"><small>12:17 EST - <a href="mailto:hermana@gameznet.com">Hermana</a></small></font><br>
      <br><blockquote>EverQuest Technical Support phone lines and Live Chat will be closed May 27th in observance of the Memorial Day holiday. <br>Normal Technical Support hours will resume on May 28th, 8:30am to 5:30 P.M. Pacific Time. </blockquote></font></p>
